title.rendered: STEDI SWITCH PANEL HOLDER HOUSING FOR ROCKER SWITCHES

content.rendered:
Rocker Switch Panels Holders

DETAILS

Switch holders compatible with most common rocker switches which are 36mm x 26mm. Our switch panels are modular, so if more slots are required at any time they are easily expandable.

DIMENSIONS 

Dimensions of 2 x end pieces together 52mm (H) x 52.5mm (W).

Each center holder adds 27mm in width.

Select your desired configuration from the drop down box above the “Add to Cart” button.

SPECIFICATIONS

ABS Plastic Modular Design

 

WHAT’S IN THE BOX

Rocker Switch Holder(s)
